# api-gateway (Cloudflare Workers) local secrets, loaded by `wrangler dev`.
# Copy to `.dev.vars` (git-ignored) and fill in as bindings/secrets grow.
#
# In production, set secrets with:  wrangler secret put <NAME>
# Non-secret config goes in wrangler.jsonc under `vars`.
#
# No secrets are required today — the gateway serves the public ApiService.
# CORS_ORIGINS and UPSTREAM_URL (src/index.ts) are non-secret runtime vars —
# set them in wrangler.jsonc `vars` per environment, not here.
#
# Example (uncomment when you add an upstream service binding token):
# API_UPSTREAM_TOKEN=""
